description: Chris Fleming, Chip Coffey, Rosemary Ellen Guiley, and Karyn Reece all join Darkness Radio after the passing of Psychic/Medium Peter James to talk about the topic of the perception of Psychic/Mediums on both TV and in the general public in the year 2007!
